{"tid":245744,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"[真心求答]你地點寫個「發」字？","createTime":"2017-05-16T13:10:51.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-17T03:06:18.000Z","uid":38203,"like":58,"dislike":39,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"73735decafeeda74d729c6fcd8ff88955d5bca21","tid":245744,"uid":38203,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-16T13:10:51.000Z","msg":"今日阿妹（讀緊小一） 派功課返黎<br />\n佢本生字書比老師圈住左個「發」字話寫錯左<br />\n<br />\n右上角要穿出去，但我老豆老母同我學都係無穿出去<br />\n<br />\n你地又係點寫？係咪兩個寫法都啱<br />\n定係真係寫錯左？<br />\n<br />\n個老師話寫法2先正確<br />\n<br />\n寫法1  比正評<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/682ocsn9\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2F682ocsn9&h=dad84c36&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n寫法2  比負評<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/0m46qp8d\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2F0m46qp8d&h=acc24843&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"c6fa58837ca348bd652d12f4a6379b2b5b273ef1","tid":245744,"uid":100760,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-16T13:12:45.000Z","msg":"呢啲濕鳩嘢小學先捉架姐<br />\n求撚其啦"},{"pid":"5871234b5cc6d5400fc730ca4647e97c51736139","tid":245744,"uid":1799,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-16T13:22:42.000Z","msg":"小學d 19老師最鍾意捉d無聊野"},{"pid":"2c472acea033b1169179fb5cfc77d9a0fcbb7d84","tid":245744,"uid":101804,"like":1,"dislike":50,"score":-49,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-16T13:28:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/05/16/212813_95344f04e4006615d9d6ec2fad182ece.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F05%2F16%2F212813_95344f04e4006615d9d6ec2fad182ece.jpg&h=17bcb57c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n會唔會少個煩惱"},{"pid":"ca91d2e79917fb2071fb3eb199f524e94d0a7298","tid":245744,"uid":7125,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-16T13:30:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/05/16/212813_95344f04e4006615d9